Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(390,210)\frz5.24\fad(300,0)\bord1}小\N千\N运\N动\N会\N的\N时\N候\N会\N很\N有\N用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有工夫去听你的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\bord1\frz16.977\pos(402,435)\fad(300,0)}敬\N爱\N诶\N那\N就\N没\N办\N法\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的二年级和三年级不是有很多活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最难得最开心的这两年 尽量不要把关系好的人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是人之常情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之常情...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个超有型的男老师这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有型？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系到底好不好 看上一年怎么会不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没做够一年班主任吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个超有型的男老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫荒井一市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日后成为大总统的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费我的时间和巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们关系真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受这两年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥的存在就是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信哥没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自夸了半天再说这种话 无语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算交女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有喜欢的女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有了吧 有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道什么叫做委婉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊 如果是我认识的 可以帮帮你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 这种事情不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要别人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我喜欢的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想让她第一个知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对矢野说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这真是没辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是绝对忍受不了第三者随便介入的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这本来也是当事人自己的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样 他们还是错过了时机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能说是缘尽于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 草药角
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他还在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播下了很多种子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为他已经回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要无法呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好久没有两人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 这种时候以前都是怎么和他相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又分到了同一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜 座位隔得好远 没什么机会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 他是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到毕业之前 都会在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却希望 能更加开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到毕业为止 都能和风早在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份喜悦 让我希望能跟多的和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在等什么人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直毫无根据的认为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男生中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是距离黑沼最近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也不见得是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太自作多情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...这...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然听到这种话 你也很不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么样回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的答案 都会有特殊的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意外的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:26.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}どうか今だけは振り向かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:39.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}夕暮れさわぐ風　触れそうな距離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:52.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を見つめてる　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:59.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}君が好きで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:05.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}君が好きで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:11.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}叶わない恋でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}傷ついてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:19.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}何度でも伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:23.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}君に届け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:26.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}这一刻 请你不要回头看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:39.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}在傍晚摇曳的风中 近在咫尺的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:52.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}我一直 凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:59.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:05.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}一直喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:11.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}即使这份恋情永远也不能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}即使会让我受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:19.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}我也想一次又一次的让你感受到这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:23.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}好想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\3c&H000007&\c&HF3F3F3&\pos(578,339)\fn汉仪丫丫体简}忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要独占的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是如此的遥远 就像那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 忘记吧
